profile:
Hello, I'm Jakob.  I started out working with my dad as a kid doing small projects around the house, Now after gaining lots of experience through friends and family, as well as doing other jobs for customers along the way.  So now here I am hoping to bring my expertise and knowledge to make your homes what you dream a reality. 

We combine our industry knowledge, the highest quality building supplies and equipment, and our dedication to deliver exceptional service to our clients. We will stay in touch, keeping you up to date on both the paperwork and renovation process.
services: Kitchen Remodel or Renovation, Repair Expertise, Flooring, Painting, Wood Flooring Refinish & Install, Tile Installation, Radiant Flooring Heating, Vinyl Sheet Flooring,
